ZH: 我正在路边摊吃早餐。
EN: I am having breakfast at a roadside stall.

ZH: 我喜欢逛夜市摊位。
EN: I enjoy strolling around night market stalls.

ZH: 他在摊上展示自己的手工艺品。
EN: He is displaying his handicrafts on the stall.

ZH: 她在摊位上忙着处理订单。
EN: She is busy dealing with orders at the stall.

ZH: 这家摊位卖的炸鸡非常好吃。
EN: The fried chicken sold at this stall is delicious.

ZH: 昨天我买了一件衣服，是在摊上砍的价。
EN: Yesterday I bought a piece of clothing and haggled the price at the stall.

ZH: 他每天晚上都会去摊位吃个夜宵。
EN: He goes to the stall for a late-night snack every night.

ZH: 路边摊上的水果很新鲜。
EN: The fruits at the roadside stall are very fresh.

ZH: 这个摊位上卖的鲜花非常漂亮。
EN: The flowers sold at this stall are very beautiful.

ZH: 他开了一个摊位，卖各种小吃。
EN: He opened a stall, selling all kinds of snacks.

ZH: 我在夜市上的摊位上买了一块手链。
EN: I bought a bracelet from the stall at the night market.

ZH: 这个摊位上的衣服很便宜。
EN: The clothes at this stall are very cheap.

ZH: 姐姐在小摊位上买了一本漫画书。
EN: My older sister bought a comic book from a small stall.

ZH: 我正在摊上买点水果。
EN: I am buying some fruits from the stall.

ZH: 这个摊位的蔬菜看起来很新鲜。
EN: The vegetables at this stall look very fresh.

ZH: 爸爸在摊位上买了一瓶自家酿的果酒。
EN: Dad bought a bottle of homemade fruit wine from the stall.

ZH: 这家摊位卖的炒面非常好吃。
EN: The fried noodles sold at this stall are delicious.

ZH: 他正在学做摊位上的小吃。
EN: He is learning to make the snacks sold at the stall.

ZH: 我在这个摊位上买了一束红玫瑰送给妈妈。
EN: I bought a bouquet of red roses from this stall to give to my mom.

ZH: 这个摊位上卖的糖葫芦很受欢迎。
EN: The candied haws sold at this stall are very popular.
